The second season of Hataraku Maou-sama! MgRonald’s best demon lord worker is back, climbing the corporate ladder to become ruler of Earth. But Maou’s plans of domination might need to be put on hold when a small girl claims to be his and Emi’s child! (Source: Crunchyroll)
The second season of Princess Connect! Re:Dive.

The story follows a unambitious introverted middle school student called Saike Kuzushiro. After witnessing the death of his childhood friend, Mikan Karatachi, in a road accident. He cries out to God and after a fall, Saike wakes up in bed the previous morning, the day of the accident. Will history repeat? Can he save Mikan? What power does he have to change the future? Included one-shots: Volume 3: The Negatibrain

After being beat up and put into a coma by eight of his classmates at Nun'Gwang Middle school, Se'young woke up after nine long months and found out that his father committed suicide by self-immolation in an attempt to get justice for what happened to him.
As a result, the investigation re-opened and that attackers who tried to sweep it under the rug received a proper sentence for their crimes. But Se'young was unable to assuage the anger and fear he felt for the unjust world. Se'young thoroughly hid himself from this sort of world.
The sun would rise and set, the seasons changed, and not once did he step outside of his home. But one day, a sudden and strange sound enticed him to open the door…
Embedded in the center of the rooftop was a gigantic blade emblazoned with the words “War Sword” and with it, came the whispers of a God.

div.span: Turbulent Adventurers are Introverted, Observant, Feeling, Prospecting and Turbulent. Adventurers are flexible and charming, always ready to explore and experience something new. They tend to have open minds, approaching life, new experiences, and people with grounded warmth.
Likely prefers fewer, yet deep and meaningful, social interactions and feels drawn to calmer environments.
Likely pragmatic and down-to-earth, with a strong focus on what is happening or very likely to happen.
Likely values emotional expression and sensitivity, prioritizing empathy, social harmony, and cooperation.
Likely very good at improvising and adapting. Tends to be flexible and values novelty above stability.
Likely self-conscious, sensitive to stress, success-driven, perfectionistic, and eager to improve.
